This is the README file for the rfbconnect package.

This software comes with ABSOLUTELY NO WARRANTY.  See the file COPYING for
details.

The rfbconnect.pl(1) attempts to open a VNC viewer to an RFB service listed
by an RFB SRV DNS record.  The following environmental variables are
understood:

    $VNCVIEWER_CMD  The name of the program to invoke as the viewer.
                    Defaults to 'vncviewer'.

   $VNCVIEWER_OPTS  The options to pass to the vnc viewer program.
                    Defaults to an empty string.

